{"id":259879,"date":[{"year":1952,"month":3,"day":6}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"文化广场","column":"","genre":"","count":"409","ytitle":"","mtitle":"三反运动橱窗诗抄","ftitle":"","authors":["汪受善"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪受善"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、“攻守同盟”靠不住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“攻守同盟”靠不住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贪污分子别顽固，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪里埋人不长久，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不定早晚总得露。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的诡计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早已破产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的材料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早被掌握，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快坦白多检举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争取立功把罪赎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、坦白比被检举好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贪污分子要记牢:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坦白比被检举好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不坦白他坦白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞒来瞒去瞒不了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁早坦白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是光明大道；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若再顽固，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有死路一条。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、警告“大老虎”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大老虎”，“大老虎”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你别装糊涂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的花招玩不了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众眼睛遮不住。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快坦白，别再顽固!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快坦白，别再顽固!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有彻底坦白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才是唯一出路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四、别装蒜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贪污犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别装蒜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的花招已完蛋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快坦白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还不晚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再顽固，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就法办!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五、坚决撕破他的脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奸商一副丑嘴脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑里藏刀好阴险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当面说人话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背后昧心眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许奸商再骗人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决撕破他的脸!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六、过街老鼠人人打"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过街老鼠人人打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奸商罪行要揭发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打倒奸商除坏蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设咱们新国家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七、打他一个下马威"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打呀打，追呀追，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奸商心肠黑又黑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打虎英雄齐下手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打他一个下马威!"}]}